Always follow BPA_STANDARD.md and PROJECT_CONTEXT.md.
Never change fixed ports (API 3000, Next.js 3100–3105).
Do not redesign UI; follow WowDash patterns.
Never overwrite existing code without merging; avoid deletions.
Prefer update-only patches and include exact apply steps.
Confirm affected files (touch points) before implementing changes.

Backend Prisma/migrations: follow backend-api docs/PRISMA_MIGRATION_NON_DESTRUCTIVE_POLICY.md (no reset, no db push on that DB, new migrations + migrate deploy, integrity check).
